Share Context: Wordpress Context

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/main.py ListMySites

---
Name: Get Site
Description: Get information about a site in Wordpress.com
Credential: ./credential
Share Context: Wordpress Context
Param: site_id_or_domain: The id or domain of the site

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/main.py GetSite

---
Name: Create Post
Description: Create a post for a site in Wordpress.com
Credential: ./credential
Share Context: Wordpress Context
Param: site_id_or_domain: The id or domain of the site
Param: title: The title of the post, defaults to "Untitled"
Param: content: The content of the post, defaults to empty.
Param: status: The status of the post, defaults to "publish". 

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/main.py CreatePost

---
Name: List Posts
Description: List all posts for a site in Wordpress.com
Credential: ./credential
Share Context: Wordpress Context
Param: site_id_or_domain: The id or domain of the site

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/main.py ListPosts

